  "frame_eqs": "zoom = 1;\nwarp = 0;\nrot = 0;\nsx = 1;\nsy = 1;\ndx = 0;\ndy = 0;\n\n\nvol = (bass+mid+treb)*0.25;\nvol = vol * vol;\n\nvoltime = voltime + vol * 0.1;\n\n\ntang = voltime*0.35;\nq1 = sin( tang );\nq2 = cos( tang );\n\nq3 = sin( tang * 0.58 );\nq4 = cos( tang * 0.58 );\n\nq5 = min( vol, 1.0 );\nq5 = max( q5, sin(time*0.18)*0.3+0.7);\n\nfrr = frr + 0.04;\n\nq6 = below(frr,1.0)* 10.0/255.0;//decay subtraction value\nmaindecay = sin(time*100.0)*4.0/255.0;\nmaindecay = maindecay * above(frr,1.0);\nq6 = q6 + maindecay;\nmonitor = q6;\n\nanimtime = animtime + vol * 0.2;\n\ntime = animtime;\nq7 = time - int(time);\nq7 = 2.0/3.0 - int(q7*3.0)/3.0;\n\nq8 = time/3.0 - int(time/3.0);\nq8 = 2.0/3.0 - int(q8*3.0)/3.0;",
